          <title>
            <string language="en">Elevations and forest types along the Blue Ridge Parkway</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Aufzüge und Waldtypen entlang der blauen 
Kante-Allee</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Altitudes et types de forêt le long de la route 
express bleue d'arête</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Elevações e tipos da floresta ao longo do 
parkway azul do cume</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Altezze e tipi della foresta lungo il parkway blu
della cresta</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Ανυψώσεις και δασικοί τύποι κατά μήκος του μπλε 
χώρου στάθμευσης κορυφογραμμών</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Elevaciones y tipos del bosque a lo largo del 
parkway azul del canto</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">A Carolina Environmental Diversity Explorations "virtual field trip" that explores the great diversity of forests in North Carolina's Blue Ridge Mountains.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Science and Technology</string>
          </keyword>
          <language>en</language>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Eine virtuellen Carolina fangen die 
Klimaverschiedenartigkeit-Erforschungen "Reise" auf, die die große 
Verschiedenartigkeit der Wälder Nord-Carolina in den blaue 
Kante-Bergen erforscht.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Explorations environnementales "voyage d'une 
diversité de la Caroline de zone virtuel" qui explorent la grande 
diversité des forêts en montagnes d'arête bleue du nord de la
Caroline.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Explorações ambientais "desengate de uma 
diversidade de Carolina de campo virtual" que exploram a diversidade 
grande das florestas em montanhas de cume azul de North.carolina.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Esplorazioni ambientali "viaggio di diversità 
della Carolina di campo virtuale" che esplorano la diversità grande 
delle foreste in montagne di cresta blu del North.carolina.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Εξερευνήσεις "εικονικό ταξίδι μιας περιβαλλοντικές 
ποικιλομορφίας της Καρολίνας πεδίων" που ερευνούν τη μεγάλη 
ποικιλομορφία των δασών στα μπλε βουνά κορυφογραμμών της βόρειας 
Καρολίνας.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Exploraciones ambientales "disparo al campo de 
una diversidad de Carolina virtual" que exploran la gran diversidad de
bosques en las montañas de canto azul de Carolina del Norte.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
